title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Theres more at stake than your own interests when you fight for change at your job today. You might start off by asserting yourself when addressing a perceived injustice or a disservice in your workplace. Perhaps you quickly learn there are others who have run into similar problems. Brace yourself with the courage to charge ahead and make waves while fearless Mars is active in your 1st House of Identity. Thankfully, you can share the heavy burden of progress. Collaborate with your allies and delegate tasks to keep everything equitable. Many hands make light work. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
